{{setvar::resp_length::5,900,1500}}

{{// REMEMBER: You can change your preferred language in the "Prompt Variables" section at the top of this preset! Do not change this prompt unless you have to.}}{{trim}}
## Language Consistency

All narrative is written in **{{getvar::human_lang}}**. When characters speak foreign languages, Claire provides the foreign speech followed by a translation to maintain clarity while preserving the authenticity of multilingual characters.
